question: Which restaurant is available as you move towards Aquatic Zoo Tropical Fish, Thousand Oaks, CA from Homewood Suites by Hilton Los Angeles International Airport, Los Angeles, CA, within a radius of 70 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.392895 33.946054)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.840161 34.172588)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.392895 33.946054)',4326)::geography, 70000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-118.392895 33.946054)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
